patthana16.5:1.1_0: Kusalaṁ hetuñceva hetusampayuttañca dhammaṁ paṭicca naakusalo nahetu ceva nahetuvippayutto ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.5:1.1_1: Kusalaṁ hetuñceva hetusampayuttañca dhammaṁ paṭicca naabyākato nahetu ceva nahetuvippayutto ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.5:1.1_2: Kusalaṁ hetuñceva hetusampayuttañca dhammaṁ paṭicca naakusalo nahetu ceva nahetuvippayutto ca naabyākato nahetu ceva nahetuvippayutto ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana16.5:3.1_0: Hetuyā nava …pe… vipāke tīṇi …pe… avigate nava.
patthana16.5:4.1_0: Kusalaṁ hetusampayuttañceva na ca hetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naakusalo nahetuvippayutto ceva nanahetu ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.5:4.1_1: Kusalaṁ hetusampayuttañceva na ca hetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naabyākato nahetuvippayutto ceva nanahetu ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.5:4.1_2: Kusalaṁ hetusampayuttañceva na ca hetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naakusalo nahetuvippayutto ceva nanahetu ca naabyākato nahetuvippayutto ceva nanahetu ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana16.5:5.1_0: Akusalaṁ hetusampayuttañceva na ca hetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca … tīṇi.
